nd heavier bikes along with providing better modulation, consistent power, and lower maintenance. That includes new brake pads, a new mineral oil, new 2.3mm thick rotors, an E-Caliper, new CNC brake adapters, new 5mm brake hoses, and ergonomic lever blades.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/23144225/Slate-EVO_EVOlution-Continues-Info-Flyer-copy.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/23144225/Slate-EVO_EVOlution-Continues-Info-Flyer-copy.jpg\" alt=\"TRP Slate EVO brakes\" width=\"2400\" height=\"1500\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/23144225/Slate-EVO_EVOlution-Continues-Info-Flyer-copy.jpg 2400w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/23144225/Slate-EVO_EVOlution-Continues-Info-Flyer-copy-297x186.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/23144225/Slate-EVO_EVOlution-Continues-Info-Flyer-copy-800x500.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/23144225/Slate-EVO_EVOlution-Continues-Info-Flyer-copy-120x75.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/23144225/Slate-EVO_EVOlution-Continues-Info-Flyer-copy-768x480.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/23144225/Slate-EVO_EVOlution-Continues-Info-Flyer-copy-1536x960.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/23144225/Slate-EVO_EVOlution-Continues-Info-Flyer-copy-2048x1280.jpg 2048w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/23144225/Slate-EVO_EVOlution-Continues-Info-Flyer-copy-696x435.jpg 696w,https://bik